{"tid":738040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[砌生豬肉]【九巴鎅椅】男子准保釋候訊　官質疑控方乏證據","createTime":"2018-07-11T08:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T12:56:08.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3abc0b53eb7073f69e7ff441acdb5afdb33e8b","tid":738040,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:44:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180711/s00001/1531295996281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180711%2Fs00001%2F1531295996281&d=JTRu4UmWOKpqXX3Vlp%2FPAcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=33066b55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180711%2Fs00001%2F1531295996281&h=b8082323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180711/s00001/1531295996281</a><br />\n<br />\n25歲男子涉嫌早前在九巴上以鎅刀損毀一張座椅，經警方調查後控以一項刑事損壞罪。案件今於觀塘裁判法院提堂，控方申請毋須答辯，以待警方進一步調查，押後至8月22日再訊。男子獲准以2000元保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>被告黃彥澤（25歲）報稱任職設計師，被控於本月3日，於98D九巴上損毀一張椅。裁判官向控方提出質疑，指沒證據顯示該損毀由被告持鎅刀造成。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，控方目前依靠從被告手機中找到一張被𠝹爛的九巴椅子相片，以及從巴士閉路電視中，找出坐在涉事椅子上的前一位乘客，確認椅子本來完好無損，以此推論被告涉案。</strong>"},{"pid":"6768e23a96c2f5d9be0114d0acc18685aed12d2c","tid":738040,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"前面話張凳無爛，就係你整爛"},{"pid":"d10ee1aef3f13a535797a6cdc4d77a36a4135d65","tid":738040,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">找出坐在涉事椅子上的前一位乘客，確認椅子本來完好無損，以此推論被告涉案</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係9屈，下次邊到有命案發生你係最後一條友行過就告9你謀殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37470c5a4250b028d8e933186c618a96e268f6ed","tid":738040,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d10ee1aef3f13a535797a6cdc4d77a36a4135d65","tid